-- Pennsylvania Region 1 - Philadelphia
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'PA1-100', 'Cardiac Arrest - Adult', 'Cardiac', 'High-quality CPR. Defibrillation. Epinephrine 1mg IV/IO q3-5min. Amiodarone 300mg then 150mg for refractory VF/VT. Consider sodium bicarbonate, calcium for specific indications.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Pennsylvania Region 1 - Philadelphia' AND c.state = 'Pennsylvania' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'PA1-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'Cincinnati Stroke Scale. Last known well time. Glucose check. Rapid transport to comprehensive stroke center. Pre-notification required.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Pennsylvania Region 1 - Philadelphia' AND c.state = 'Pennsylvania' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'PA1-300', 'Trauma - Major', 'Trauma', 'C-spine immobilization. Hemorrhage control with tourniquets. IV access. Rapid transport to Level I trauma center. TXA 1g IV for significant hemorrhage.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Pennsylvania Region 1 - Philadelphia' AND c.state = 'Pennsylvania' LIMIT 1;

-- Pennsylvania Region 5 - Pittsburgh
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'PA5-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'CPR, defibrillation, ACLS medications. Consider mechanical CPR for prolonged transport. Post-arrest targeted temperature management.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Pennsylvania Region 5 - Southwest PA Allegheny Washington Westmoreland Fayette Greene' AND c.state = 'Pennsylvania' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'PA5-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'Stroke assessment. Document onset. Glucose. Transport to stroke center within 60 minutes.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Pennsylvania Region 5 - Southwest PA Allegheny Washington Westmoreland Fayette Greene' AND c.state = 'Pennsylvania' LIMIT 1;

-- Illinois - Chicago
INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'IL-CHI-100', 'Cardiac Arrest', 'Cardiac', 'Chicago Fire Department protocol: CPR, defibrillation, ACLS drugs. Consider ECMO for refractory arrest.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Illinois Region 11 - Chicago Cook' AND c.state = 'Illinois' LIMIT 1;

INSERT INTO protocolChunks (countyId, protocolNumber, protocolTitle, section, content, sourcePdfUrl, createdAt)
SELECT c.id, 'IL-CHI-200', 'Stroke', 'Neurological', 'Stroke alert activation. Last known well. Glucose. Rapid transport to designated stroke center.', '', NOW()
FROM counties c WHERE c.name = 'Illinois Region 11 - Chicago Cook' AND c.state = 'Illinois' LIMIT 1;
